| 1  | m1.tiny   | 512       | 0    | 0         |      | 1     | 1.0         |
| 2  | m1.small  | 2048      | 10   | 20        |      | 1     | 1.0         |
| 3  | m1.medium | 4096      | 10   | 40        |      | 2     | 1.0         |
